{"tid":1209941,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今日係前線親身感受到真係好恐怖","createTime":"2019-06-12T12:39:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T14:50:00.000Z","uid":240178,"like":197,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"c72d844bade8e992e80347e5f1d085741e311f42","tid":1209941,"uid":240178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T12:39:16.000Z","msg":"「長文」<br />\n今朝6:30分到左金鐘 身為一個香港人打算出一分力 因為69冇出黎都有少少後悔。一到左就同其他義士一齊佔領左夏愨道，見證住其他義士一齊佔領哂所有馬路真係覺得好感動，心入面燃起左一點希望。一齊捱到今日立法會延遲，中途啲狗一路就係到隔一陣就射下水。<br />\n其實中途真係有啲攰，因為前一晚根本訓唔到，差唔多3點幾先訓5點幾又出門口。但見到大家都係到堅持，我就決定繼續努力堅守。<br />\n一路直到三點幾，（我個時都係係前面既位置 大概第四五排），警方好似開始有行動，（我係絲）生得唔係好高睇唔到前面發生咩事，只係聽到其他義士叫開遮，啲狗又射水，一路向前又向後咁，突然間我地防線推前左，當時又有好多其他比較驚既義士向後走左，所以連隔離馬路既前面都好空曠，於是乎我同兩個朋友就一齊行去左邊補空缺（當時都有幾位前鋒受左傷退下左）<br />\n而當時我地基本上可以有既裝備都戴哂，眼罩頭盔袖套保鮮紙口罩同埋我地所謂既武器-遮。齊心開遮諗住可以保護到自己，點知啲狗突然發難搏老命咁掉催淚彈同噴胡椒噴霧，當時大家都好驚好痛咁向後跑，情況真係好混亂，開始人推人。<br />\n而呢個時候因爲我企第三排所以中哂所有野，即刻跟住其他人走但係塊臉同手臂真係好撚痛，跟住呼吸開始好困難睇野又睇唔到，個個情景真係好似世界末日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />其間被撞到跌低左同朋友失散左，又好混亂既情況下比義士拉返起身繼續走，點知跑到一半又比人撞跌左，跟住今次自己爬返起身個下已經好暈好驚。<br />\n離開左個個煙霧瀰漫既地方之後行到wingwing地 有兩位巴打（太辛苦睇唔到樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）攬住左我比左啲生理鹽水同埋啲濕左唔知咩氧既毛巾我放係個鼻到，終於冇咁辛苦，但隻手同面真係好痛。 好多謝拉起我扶過我既你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後嚇到半死又失散左既我最後離開左金鐘 好對唔住各位 小女真係好撚唔舒服要走先，希望留守既你地唔好再受傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望中槍同昏迷個幾位義士會冇事 香港唔可以失去你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋 好希望係現場既義士朋友唔好再掉自己啲物資啦，今日見到你地掉遮掉頭盔真係好撚on9啊！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後好想講句，黑警林鄭我屌哂你地老母！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b1268c6de817bf53485193e4430206cf4889dc8","tid":1209941,"uid":77740,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T12:49:08.000Z","msg":"多謝你，辛苦曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59f3ecd1c3e9bbd660851ca6fa6f7dd2bc1783f5","tid":1209941,"uid":240178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b1268c6de817bf53485193e4430206cf4889dc8","tid":1209941,"uid":77740,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T12:49:08.000Z","msg":"多謝你，辛苦曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T13:21:14.000Z","msg":"一離開現場電話收到消息見到有人中槍就又好嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7eed840615c230d30213521e9743d82360935cd3","tid":1209941,"uid":17008,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T13:32:23.000Z","msg":"我都見 係咁掉物資<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有咩用 好難搵返黎<br />\n你話番茄都叫有效果 而家夏天 好快成身臭  無得換衫著成日 精神層面打擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6283286f6a03fff867248f2896e7eb7af72a8b1","tid":1209941,"uid":161098,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T13:42:54.000Z","msg":"多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65f8108d505a8d6500fa908bb06f0813df6c500e","tid":1209941,"uid":240178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7eed840615c230d30213521e9743d82360935cd3","tid":1209941,"uid":17008,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T13:32:23.000Z","msg":"我都見 係咁掉物資<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有咩用 好難搵返黎<br />\n你話番茄都叫有效果 而家夏天 好快成身臭  無得換衫著成日 精神層面打擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:02:16.000Z","msg":"傳啲遮同裝備比佢地唔係要佢地掉入去比啲狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2e6720fa217e59866cbff49d1315810cb1010e6","tid":1209941,"uid":13738,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:03:48.000Z","msg":"困左係商場入面再放煙...仲恐怖<br />\n上又封，大門又封，邊到都走唔到<br />\n已經打定輸數"},{"pid":"6226379454865fede9e6aec09d6e97730395f74d","tid":1209941,"uid":254114,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:05:15.000Z","msg":"Thx sis"},{"pid":"cc12b7c4940a51e38954792a2004f0713e7136d4","tid":1209941,"uid":240178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f6283286f6a03fff867248f2896e7eb7af72a8b1","tid":1209941,"uid":161098,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T13:42:54.000Z","msg":"多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:05:54.000Z","msg":"禁錯左負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我都係好後悔冇繼續留低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但係前線真係成個地獄咁好撚驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4de35613096356a5fe098586108d004ed94b79af","tid":1209941,"uid":49918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:07:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ada061c910c9f80099b47c9d7120fa0e3adbe961","tid":1209941,"uid":240178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d2e6720fa217e59866cbff49d1315810cb1010e6","tid":1209941,"uid":13738,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:03:48.000Z","msg":"困左係商場入面再放煙...仲恐怖<br />\n上又封，大門又封，邊到都走唔到<br />\n已經打定輸數"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:09:44.000Z","msg":"未輸架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />長久戰黎架"},{"pid":"0bfd78f41f873c5c62f3cfcc22f2bce7b8448d8f","tid":1209941,"uid":24284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:12:51.000Z","msg":"頭盔都唔帶?"},{"pid":"aeb7f2e4ea9dc34f14b073ef4e5298b8823cc92e","tid":1209941,"uid":240178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0bfd78f41f873c5c62f3cfcc22f2bce7b8448d8f","tid":1209941,"uid":24284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:12:51.000Z","msg":"頭盔都唔帶?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:18:22.000Z","msg":"上面咪話左有 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />塊臉一樣咁痛"},{"pid":"ce0f60c2f10389e25ada39662bd1bdf9738a5e3f","tid":1209941,"uid":22360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:19:31.000Z","msg":"注意自己精神狀態，可能有ptsd，盡早休息先！"},{"pid":"ae66eff5f49f89256305d0acf069f18088c1fb0d","tid":1209941,"uid":24284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aeb7f2e4ea9dc34f14b073ef4e5298b8823cc92e","tid":1209941,"uid":240178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0bfd78f41f873c5c62f3cfcc22f2bce7b8448d8f","tid":1209941,"uid":24284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:12:51.000Z","msg":"頭盔都唔帶?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:18:22.000Z","msg":"上面咪話左有 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />塊臉一樣咁痛"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:20:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我問你係咪發夢夢見呀，唔好問我住，google下咩叫戴頭盔先"},{"pid":"1761db9003f097085b25c62c5a2d0c875fcc5d5d","tid":1209941,"uid":62305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:21:03.000Z","msg":"龍和道比狗清得超快..."},{"pid":"73679b7be985e03654f556d6060f7fc6ca67c58b","tid":1209941,"uid":227823,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cc12b7c4940a51e38954792a2004f0713e7136d4","tid":1209941,"uid":240178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f6283286f6a03fff867248f2896e7eb7af72a8b1","tid":1209941,"uid":161098,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T13:42:54.000Z","msg":"多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:05:54.000Z","msg":"禁錯左負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我都係好後悔冇繼續留低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但係前線真係成個地獄咁好撚驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:22:22.000Z","msg":"辛苦你啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你比好多人都勇敢"},{"pid":"83676a98267c209b4d077962e795660b0f903845","tid":1209941,"uid":22069,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:23:06.000Z","msg":"多謝你<br />\n女仔都行得前過我。。屌<br />\n當年企過第一行食左好多野驚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef5ab5bfbeaef22e9b2d057ff319ab6c3185b612","tid":1209941,"uid":40397,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:24:03.000Z","msg":"感謝你為香港付出"},{"pid":"bad6da868d7e5dc25d77c5762b07855264d6cbad","tid":1209941,"uid":117871,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:27:06.000Z","msg":"多謝你，好勇敢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好好休息！"},{"pid":"31fb318c9371fa5a3f19d7cd9ba69fc0404c7583","tid":1209941,"uid":158984,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:35:56.000Z","msg":"我都係第一次去呢啲地方，今朝係夏愨道望到有人比警察打已經驚驚地，再有人嗌紅旗係咁跑差啲同朋友失散已經開始驚驚地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後無耐同朋友失散左我就幫手係天橋派下物資咁，派到個物資站比人搬左落去就去左食野<br />\n食完野就收到消息準備衝立法會，就去搵啲物資睇下幫唔幫到手<br />\n本身諗住搵第二個朋友，點知收到消息開始亂就驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係到周圍搵物資睇下有咩幫到手<br />\n最後黑旗我好驚我淆底走左，聽到佢地係咁叫我地唔好走我都好唔好意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n媽咪，同事同親戚知我得返自己都叫我唔好留低，對唔住我怕死我走左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我自問無咁既勇氣面對即將發生既混亂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇到好多消息我都好驚但又好嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n望到每個人好團結好齊心好有愛好感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聽日會變到點我唔知，如果聽日有咩物資需要既我會幫手架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申：份工無得話就放，今日咁岩放假先黎到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81ebf1155b7aefcf0cf075011280f8934aea4f07","tid":1209941,"uid":176121,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:37:51.000Z","msg":"多謝你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecf369e0503c2e03685fcde550679f5186a87f9c","tid":1209941,"uid":53034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:39:12.000Z","msg":"樓主是咪發夢呀"},{"pid":"2c66f73590441b12e4e4d4b66a84d4334e86666e","tid":1209941,"uid":240178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae66eff5f49f89256305d0acf069f18088c1fb0d","tid":1209941,"uid":24284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aeb7f2e4ea9dc34f14b073ef4e5298b8823cc92e","tid":1209941,"uid":240178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0bfd78f41f873c5c62f3cfcc22f2bce7b8448d8f","tid":1209941,"uid":24284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:12:51.000Z","msg":"頭盔都唔帶?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:18:22.000Z","msg":"上面咪話左有 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />塊臉一樣咁痛"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:20:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我問你係咪發夢夢見呀，唔好問我住，google下咩叫戴頭盔先"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:47:04.000Z","msg":"補充<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />發夢既時候感受到好痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"716cacd757aa2df63fd25c2d0573b4913b7a1af1","tid":1209941,"uid":240178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ecf369e0503c2e03685fcde550679f5186a87f9c","tid":1209941,"uid":53034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:39:12.000Z","msg":"樓主是咪發夢呀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:48:00.000Z","msg":"係啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />個夢嚇到我唔記得講"}]}